modShortDescription: Honey can be very difficult to find early game. This mod increases the chance of honey dropping from tree stumps.
modDescription:
Honey can be very difficult to find early game. This mod increases the chance of [honey](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/7-days-to-die-food/) dropping from tree stumps and also slightly increases the probability of tree stumps spawning in the world. That part requires a new map to see results for.
